00:11.777 --> 00:13.980
I need your signature. I want to
take out a loan against the business.

00:14.047 --> 00:16.717
No, no, no. No way.

00:16.786 --> 00:18.554
Everything seems to be in order.

00:18.622 --> 00:23.060
Don't need the loan anymore,
buddy boy. I got an extension.

00:23.128 --> 00:24.596
This is really bad.

00:24.663 --> 00:26.298
How come I don't feel guilty?

00:26.366 --> 00:28.568
We need to stop doing this.

00:28.636 --> 00:30.438
You're not going back to him, are you?

00:30.505 --> 00:31.339
He's my husband.

00:31.407 --> 00:32.641
So you deserve better.

00:32.708 --> 00:34.610
You won't ever make me happy.

00:34.677 --> 00:37.680
