06:40.653 --> 06:44.526
A few years ago, we found out
that Matt was actually my son, and

06:44.594 --> 06:47.195
he decided to beat the shit
out of me in the scrub room.

06:47.263 --> 06:50.798
I think that was the worst.

06:53.835 --> 06:57.871
Usually, when couples seek therapy,

06:57.938 --> 07:01.309
it's when things are at their
bleakest, when all hope seems

07:01.376 --> 07:06.681
