07:15.523 --> 07:17.290
Do you love Dr. Troy?

07:17.358 --> 07:23.363
I do. He's like the brother I never had.

07:23.431 --> 07:25.531
Sometimes family can be very

07:25.599 --> 07:29.935
difficult. When we describe
a friend as a family member,

07:30.003 --> 07:33.472
sometimes we're saying we love
them in spite of themselves,

07:33.539 --> 07:36.874
that we have no choice but to love them.

07:36.942 --> 07:41.245
Do you feel you have a
choice to love Dr. Troy?

07:41.313 --> 07:42.213
Of course I do.

07:43.949 --> 07:48.185
I want to try an exercise with you.

07:52.256 --> 08:02.497
I want you to draw your families. Doesn't have
to be a Degas. Just draw whatever you feel.

08:02.564 --> 08:05.199
