New York. How'd you know that?

08:40.029 --> 08:42.797
Everyone's hands are
touching except yours.

08:42.865 --> 08:45.299
You put your ex-wife in your
picture, but you didn't put me in it.

08:45.367 --> 08:46.867
Now you're judging my picture.

08:46.935 --> 08:47.935
