09:59.596 --> 10:01.196
No, you didn't tell me. What
happened a few months ago?

10:01.264 --> 10:03.031
Nothing. That's the point.

10:03.098 --> 10:05.132
This relationship never changes.

10:05.200 --> 10:06.767
I'm just waking up to the fact

10:06.835 --> 10:10.537
